name: Riley Strain
summary: The search for Riley Strain, a missing college student from Missouri, has come to a tragic end. His body was discovered in the Cumberland River in Nashville, Tennessee, on Sunday, January 29th. The cause of death is still under investigation, but no foul play is suspected. Strain's family and friends had been desperately searching for him since he went missing on January 21st. They had followed leads to several bars and had even coordinated a search party at Cheatham Dam. The recovery of Strain's body has brought some closure to his family, but it also raises questions about the circumstances surrounding his disappearance.

name: Government shutdown
summary: Congress has announced a deal to avert another federal government shutdown. The House has passed a $1.2 trillion spending bill which now moves to the Senate, where passage is expected. This agreement resolves a dispute over funding for the Department of Homeland Security (DHS). The bill also includes funding for other agencies and programs, such as the National Institutes of Health and the Federal Emergency Management Agency. A government shutdown would have significant impacts on essential services, including border security, air traffic control, and national parks. Despite the pending agreement, experts warn that government shutdowns are becoming more frequent and normalized, which raises concerns about the stability of the federal government.

name: Duquesne basketball
summary: In the 2023 NCAA Tournament, unheralded Duquesne University pulled off an upset victory against Brigham Young University (BYU). The matchup between the two schools was broadcast on CBS Sports and highlighted by the retirement of Duquesne's head coach, Keith Dambrot. Despite being considered the underdog, Duquesne managed to outlast BYU, notching their first NCAA Tournament victory since 1969. Duquesne had previously won the Atlantic 10 Championship in 2024. The historic win marked a significant achievement for the Duquesne Dukes basketball program, underscoring the parity and unpredictability of March Madness.

Despite negative reviews, the film's theatrical release has been lauded as a fitting venue for its chaotic and entertaining nature. Streaming options are also available for those who prefer to watch the remake at home.

name: NC State basketball
summary: NC State's men's basketball team had an impressive performance in the 2024 ACC Tournament. They won the tournament championship, defeating Virginia 73-65 in overtime and then beating rival North Carolina to secure an automatic bid to the NCAA Tournament. NC State's victory over UNC was particularly significant as it completed an unlikely Cinderella run for the Wolfpack. The team's head coach, Kevin Keatts, expressed his pride in the team's accomplishment, calling it an "improbable" victory. The Wolfpack will now face Texas Tech in the opening round of the NCAA Tournament on Thursday.
